<br>
First off, get a book of obulous until cleric gets to the point where she's never using Sup Heal. It's actually really nice.  I got one for 2k-ish or so.<br>
<br>
Could try for square helm -- 6 wis, extended range 3, and looks like plate, so that's kinda cool.  Haven't seen one sold in a while.  They drop in skyshrine tho, you could probably fight up to the first room of wyverns and camp there to get one once your cleric is 40 and can group with ya.  Barring that, Platinum Tiara is 35hp and 50mana, with an enhancement focus of some sort.<br>
<br>
Teacher's syllabus is cool for range..3 wis, 20 mana 20 poison IIRC.  Oakleaf girdle is a nice belt..40hp/mana.  Good for the point when you're gonna go over 200 wis.  Shissar scale cape is another 1 wis and 25 mana over the mammy cloak, shouldn't be too expensive, you could also snag one from the grey with your duo most likely.  If ya don't like that option, there's a tailored acrylia cloak that's 10 wis.<br>
<br>
Tserrina's symbol is a nice neck..5 wis, 40 mana.  Again, totally duo-able once ya hit 40.  Coldain skin gloves are only 3k-ish last time I saw, and are 6 wis 20 mana, same for boots, which will add another 35ish mana.  Breastplate is kinda hard...ya got seb scale cloak and maybe acrylia tunic to choose from.  Probably run ya another 3k or so tho.<br>
<br>
After we did all that on our little cleric, we took em to Kael and got him some plate pieces.  I'm not really sure where else to go from there, but he seems like he's doing pretty good.  Against most stuff he never runs out of mana anyway since he's only standing for 10 seconds during the fight to cast CH <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
That should keep ya busy on cheap stuff to look for anyway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usmushums.showPublicProfile?language=EN>smushums</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Steel Warrior Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 1284<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/31/02 1:24:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1219.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Making a healer to 2 box with</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=349715">www.magelo.com/eq_view_pr...num=349715</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
